## `fs.unlink`

Removes a file.

```javascript
fs.unlink('temp.txt', (err) => {
  if (err) {
    console.error('Error deleting file:', err);
  } else {
    console.log('File deleted');
  }
});
```

If the file doesn't exist, you'll get an error, so handle it.
